#Spectra
Load file
shift points by -tau
set size (8K button)
+2^n zeroes
Fourier
rephase

#T1/2D
Load file
shift points by -tau
set size (8K button)
+2^n zeroes
Fourier
rephase
matrix> region> integrate
select region around peak


#T1/Cut echo and stitch correctly 
cut out first few points, say 50us for a 150us echo tau
then use tools>swap echo and input its *shifted* tau value
then add zeroes as normal and fourier/rephase
integrate peak with about 2/3 of the peak width to ensure you get maximal signal